it's been an ongoing passion project
for almost a decade

144
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:49,259
because the immune system is just about
the most amazing and fascinating topic there is.

145
00:09:49,259 --> 00:09:52,620
So, go on a journey and get to know your own body.

146
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:57,852
From mystery organs, murder universities,
to the largest library in the universe.

147
